title: DermaNew Facial Rejuvenation System
description: Gently resurface and smooth skin. title: Diamancel Tough Buffer #11
description: Im the first to admit I wondered about this item when I first received it, but I am a true believer after just one use!  Try using this Diamond Chip Foot Buffer along with an excellent foot cream (and the Callous Rasp if needed) to get incredibly soft feet.  <br><br>Will get your feet looking pool pretty in an evening!  <br><br>Genuine diamond chips make this foot care file effective for buffing your feet to a silky smoothness.  Nickel coated fiberglass combines with diamonds for flexibility and strength in this unique foot grooming tool.  <br><br>Use on dry feet for best effects and then apply an exfoliating agent for maximum moisturizing benefits.    <br><br>Try Diamancels Callous Rasp for those little detail areas.  <br><br>Caring for your Tough Buffer is easy.  Simply clean with soap and water and a soft brush.  Rinse under running water.  For anyone with athletes foot, soak your buffer in an antibacterial solution to help kill contagious fungus.  It is NOT recommended that the tool be autoclaved.
